i khi có ai đó can thiệp. Nghi lễ sau này được gọi là \"Thảm kịch Balbagoa.\" Sau khi được Giruu cứu, cậu bé Hiiro bắt đầu học kiếm thuật để có thể trả thù cho cha mẹ mình.</p>","tmdb_id":66102,"cast":["Arisa Ogasawara","Manami Numakura","Masayuki Omoro","Shunsuke Sakuya","Mariya Ise","Yoji Ueda","Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","Mao Ichimichi","Maaya Uchida","Taiten Kusunoki","Rintaro Nishi"],"director":[],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"66102","season":1,"vote_average":7.6,"vote_count":32},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Arisa Ogasawara","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Arisa Ogasawara","tmdb_id":1246266,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iZtQW0a8Dc8B1mGh2jd8BmKMGwz.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1246266"},{"name":"Manami Numakura","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Manami Numakura","tmdb_id":1255653,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eDbMXgeTCA2D6i7894Ag43RADrk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1255653"},{"name":"Masayuki Omoro","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Masayuki Omoro","tmdb_id":1251550,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cON0G2IPZ2lrYtqb7X1HwOWBqQv.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1251550"},{"name":"Shunsuke Sakuya","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Shunsuke Sakuya","tmdb_id":1222051,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tbIQ3CFxZM9wl5S4YMwqhrs5VNS.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1222051"},{"name":"Mariya Ise","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Mariya Ise","tmdb_id":1250465,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tQWlgrlQ70biWdg7x9E75CtwsuD.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1250465"},{"name":"Yoji Ueda","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yoji Ueda","tmdb_id":1264228,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fHvIfE0Q7ab0DFlkNVFcXvTKX9y.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1264228"},{"name":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","tmdb_id":233590,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ugDwdWEXnmv43jcbnfAi4Xwi